</taxonomicName>
and an unidentified sea anemone (see 
<bibRefCitation id="8D696997FFC0FFA4FA90FE49FEDCFDD5" author="Okuno, J. &amp; Imazeki, S." pageId="16" pageNumber="101" pagination="15 - 18" refId="ref12535" refString="Okuno, J. &amp; Imazeki, S. (2008) Occurrence of Periclimenes tenuirostris Bruce, 1991 (Crustacea: Decapoda: Palaemonidae) in the northwestern Pacific, with description of its coloration in life and record of new host. Natural History Research, 10 (1), 15 - 18." type="journal article" year="2008">Okuno &amp; Imazeki 2008</bibRefCitation>
